bio: VitaDAO is a community owned collective funding early stage longevity research
impactDescription: Bridging VitaDAO to Optimism carries significant benefits for the Optimism community. By integrating the $VITA token, Optimism showcases its adaptability to diverse projects, enhancing its position as a versatile layer 2 solution. VitaDAO's primary focus is on funding early-stage longevity research. By facilitating this bridge, the Optimism community gains the opportunity to govern a longevity DAO. This empowers the community to actively participate in decisions related to longevity research funding, fostering collective responsibility. In essence, this integration not only strengthens Optimism's ecosystem but also provides its community with a unique role in shaping the future of longevity research.

lists.listName: 🧪🔬🌐🚀🧬 Decentralized Science and Biological Conservation Underrated Projects & Individuals
lists.listDescription: In this unique curation, we spotlight the unsung heroes and underappreciated projects dedicated to advancing decentralized science and fostering biological conservation efforts. Within this curation, expect to delve into a treasure trove of pioneering projects that disrupt the traditional paradigms of scientific research and conservation. From grassroots movements employing decentralized technologies to facilitate open-access research, to the endeavors of individuals working quietly but profoundly to protect and preserve our planet's biodiversity, this curation sheds light on their impactful endeavors. This curated collection, endorsed by Greenpill México, emphasizes the urgent need to regenerate biological and complex systems within traditional science. Through innovative approaches and the exploration of new use cases, the initiative strives to revolutionize scientific practices toward a more decentralized and sustainable future.
